<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA54">
<l>kāruruvak kaṇṭatteṅ kaṇṇutalē yeṅkoḷittā</l>
<l>yōruruvāy niṉṉō ṭuḻitaruvā - ṉīruruva</l>
<l>mēkattāṟceytaṉaiya mēṉiyā ṉiṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>pākattāṉ kāṇāmē paṇṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our [man with] an eye on the forehead, with a throat the colour of the rain cloud, where have you hidden?</l>
<l>We did not earlier see the one with a part possessed by you,</l>
<l>with a body that is as if made from a water-coloured cloud,</l>
<l>they one who wanders with you in one form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
